<br>
Looking over the walls, he found a sword that was shorter than the rest. &quot;A full tang katana.&quot; He took it down and strapped it to his back so that the handle was pointed down and on his right. He spent a few minutes practicing swinging the weapon, as well as sheathing and unsheating it. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bkalaberia.showUserPublicProfile?gid=knightspasr>knightspasr</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://stu.aii.edu/~job312/werespider.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle><i>~Kalaberia Citizen~</i></span><br>  Posts: 24<br> <font color=#8B4513>(7/16/03 10:20 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> a short rest?</span><hr size=1> &quot;Sleep would be good I think me and Alexander here well keep watch though for at least in this form our sense are hire and I can't say I trust anyone here now”  Cynthia looks at the already sleeping Taylee, and shakes her head.<br>
